I was really disappointed to discover that the episodes on this DVD are all included in Duck Dynasty seasons 1, 2, 3, and 4.  A waste of money!  This should have been mentioned in the product description.  Will be returning this.
I already had all the episodes of the program. These were all repeats of what I already had. I wish they would have told me.

Duck Dynasty truly is good, fun, Family Friendly viewing.  These are good episodes.  Si is a riot.  We do wish, however, that it was made clear that those of us who have already purchased all of the Seasons of Duck Dynasty already have these episodes.  These are repeat episodes which we and all who have the Seasons already own.  Disappointed because we thought it was something new and it is repeats.  Happy that clean, Family things are still being produced.

I enjoy watching Duck Dynasty on tv and now I have a dvd to watch them on vacation!  It's family-friendly and a
great dvd to watch.  You feel like you're on vacation with them!  The family makes me laugh!  The dvd arrived on
time and was in excellent condition.  I would highly recommend this dvd!  Relax and enjoy!!

The show about Hawaii was really good.  It had a couple of the same shows that I have on another DVD.  But Duck Dynasty is always a joy to watch.

I know this is reality television but it is real and truthful and honest. I love this series and I really do like this family. I think I am in love with Uncle Si. Too bad, we are both married but he is a riot. They have so much fun with each other and enjoy being a family. You don't have to worry about anything unsightly or rude words when you watch this series. This is just a good fun show to watch with your family and we need more of these for our families to view together. I have to give Willie a lot of credit, too, for being such a good sport about things. I don't think my husband would ever wear a sarong! five stars for sure.
